Description: Every year we have a massive blowout sale, that clears out the warehouse of all the junk that piles up over the year. What's left we usually blow out online, and this year is no different. We have a surplus of used electric guitars, that need to go for some early spring cleaning, to make room and way for the new 2019 models. We have about 20 guitars in total (please check our other listings) that need to go, and all of them will vary in brand and condition. Assume, unless noted, that these will need completely gone over. Some of these are ready to go, some need a little help. These might be good for a great deal on parts, a new trio of addition to your collection, or a great opportunity to clean up/set up/fix up, and resell for a nice profit! The choice is up to you! All are sold as-is, with no warranty. All 3 of these just recently had new strings put on them and a quick setup, so after a cleaning these should be ready to go. We tested them all out and all the tuners are working, pickups are working, and only a minor scratch here and there in the pots that will easily clean up. Overall in great shape and this could be a great deal for someone looking to flip a few beginner level guitars! Track Page Views With Auctiva's FREE Counter
